{
  "texts": [
    "For Wikifier and TagMe, we use the default confidence threshold with the highest recall.",
    "Table 3 presents the overall token-and entity-level performances on untyped and typed entities under four filtering scenarios.",
    "Token-level As the filtering conditions become more stringent, the accuracy increases for all three models.",
    "Namely, NC-only achieves the highest accuracy, followed by C-only and N-only, and Orig scores the lowest.",
    "TagMe exhibits the largest disparity between typed and untyped token accuracy among the three models, but this difference decreases after adding filters."
  ]
}